<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
  <div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <hr>
    <p>
    I'm a starter designer & developer living in Minsk.
    </p>
    <p>
    I have a good knowledge of front-end stuff + angular.js, git + github. I'm improving them by doing PSD to HTML and academy's laboratory works.
    </p>
    <p>
    Spend all my free time reading articles, watching videos about developing, design and doing a projects like that.
    </p>
    <p>
    By now i learn back-end based on Ruby on Rails also improving  my skills in Photoshop, Ai.
    </p> 
  </div>
  <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
    <h2>Stuff I've Build</h2>
    <hr>
    <% @projects.each do |project| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to project.title, project %></a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= project.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-3 homepage_content">
    <h2>Stuff I've Written</h2>
    <hr>
    <% @posts.each do |post| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to post.title, post %></a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div> <!-- wrapper-end -->